%head
  %title LinkedLCCN - Turning LCCNs into Linked Data
  %link{:rel=>"stylesheet", :type=>"text/css", :href=>"/css/style.css"}
%body
  %h2 Welcome to LinkedLCCN
  
  #intro
    LinkedLCCN is a service to wrap the
    %a{:href=>"http://lccn.loc.gov/"} Library of Congress' LCCN Permalink Service
    and convert it into linked data.
  %div
    Resources are generated by a series of lookups (LoC, VIAF.org, dbpedia.org, musicbrainz, linkedmbd, etc.) on the fly and stored in the Talis Platform for subsequent requests.
  %div
    A 
    %a{:href=>"http://api.talis.com/stores/rsinger-dev4/services/sparql"} SPARQL endpoint is available for querying here.
    
  